17:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. LOVO AI is best suited for voiceover for videos, multi language content, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Speechify, meanwhile, shines for reading text content aloud, accessibility, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2019, LOVO AI describes itself as \"AI voiceover and text-to-speech platform.\" Speechify, established in 2017, positions itself as \"Listen to anything with natural-sounding AI voices.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
18:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Speechify** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean LOVO AI is a poor choice — far from it. LOVO AI excels in its own right, particularly for voiceover for videos and multi language content.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value great browser extension, go with Speechify. If 500+ voices in 100 languages matters more to you, LOVO AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
